{"tid":2084972,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK新歌MV「把象神放地上」掀爭議！　印度網友氣炸：對神明不敬","createTime":"2020-06-29T14:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:42:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93b4b12ba0b87eff2222eb806d8c50c65fe210e1","tid":2084972,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK睽違1年回歸樂壇，26日發行單曲《How You Like That》，MV釋出不到24小時就打破YouTube紀錄，目前更已累積逾1.4億次點閱，但MV中的一個將印度象神（Ganesha）放在地上的畫面卻掀起爭議，引起大批印度網友不滿，認為此舉對神明不敬，要求YG娛樂道歉。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK新歌《How You Like That》MV中一段Lisa的Solo畫面掀起爭議，只見她坐在沙發上，扶手擺著神燈，畫面充滿異域風情，而一旁的地上則擺著印度的象神神像。事實上，象神是印度教中的智慧之神，印度網友認為神明不應該被擺在地上，為了尊重應該擺在比人頭部還要高的地方，但MV中卻擺在比人還低的位置，有不敬的意味。<br />\n<br />\n而《How You Like That》MV釋出後，對象神不敬的爭議越演越烈，更在Twitter出現#Ganesha 和#YGapologise的hashtag。BLACKPINK的印度官方後援會也發出聲明，表示基於尊重不同國家文化的立場下，相信此舉有冒犯象神的疑慮，已經嘗試和所屬的公司YG娛樂聯繫，希望YG能進一步做出處理。"},{"pid":"fb191357ecae82c0050b741055aa90e3dfb10191","tid":2084972,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4969/d4969871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4969%2Fd4969871.jpg&h=1671f7fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK新歌MV掀起對神明不敬的爭議。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）"},{"pid":"2dc207fb23d65341ec726f5d9420217672995339","tid":2084972,"uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"印度佬寧舍麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419b3995f1d2a2293ce09459d96f3f624d763e57","tid":2084972,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"indianlivesmatter"},{"pid":"b647486ae4dfa308cabff20af345941295584d8a","tid":2084972,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4969/4969874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4969%2F4969874.jpg&h=fcba290c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e010dd280aa77db6e3adf363cad1e6e402c60e2","tid":2084972,"uid":76632,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"呢個係泰國象神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，象徵藝術同創作靈感之神，泰國象神並不等於印度象神（智慧同財富之神）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n正如羅馬神話同希臘神話入面雖然有相同嘅神，但其實各有少少分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度人成日對號入座，做乜9啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9c57ff32633bd8502082f6c972fea25ddd8b0fc3","tid":2084972,"uid":48783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"又係印狗啲frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d9a5c81a3b5c56ac4c2cadfdc1bf3be125ca46","tid":2084972,"uid":250919,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"今日凌晨官方MV就Del左個象神啦，仲加埋4K，改埋粉色結尾字樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a9f885775abfda5e75510163ed8de94c3da4e9","tid":2084972,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e010dd280aa77db6e3adf363cad1e6e402c60e2","tid":2084972,"uid":76632,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"呢個係泰國象神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，象徵藝術同創作靈感之神，泰國象神並不等於印度象神（智慧同財富之神）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n正如羅馬神話同希臘神話入面雖然有相同嘅神，但其實各有少少分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度人成日對號入座，做乜9啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"但係